Trinity Cola.

A three-tier fermented payload compiled to a single glyph string. The heavy
Muscovado foundation, the acetic kombucha knife, and the wild ginger-bug engine
are each built up in their own vessel, liquefied, then layered back into one
bright tank in reverse so the system pours out true. Runs as Chef; serves the
product name to standard out.

Ingredients.
84 g Muscovado Sugar
82 g Charred Oak
73 g Star Anise
78 g Cinnamon
89 ml Ginger Bug
32 ml Filtered Water
67 ml Kombucha
79 g Cane Sugar
76 g Lime Zest
65 ml Almond Extract

Method.
Put Cinnamon into the mixing bowl.
Put Star Anise into the mixing bowl.
Put Charred Oak into the mixing bowl.
Put Muscovado Sugar into the mixing bowl.
Put Filtered Water into the 2nd mixing bowl.
Put Ginger Bug into the 2nd mixing bowl.
Put Muscovado Sugar into the 2nd mixing bowl.
Put Star Anise into the 2nd mixing bowl.
Put Almond Extract into the 3rd mixing bowl.
Put Lime Zest into the 3rd mixing bowl.
Put Cane Sugar into the 3rd mixing bowl.
Put Kombucha into the 3rd mixing bowl.
Liquefy contents of the mixing bowl.
Liquefy contents of the 2nd mixing bowl.
Liquefy contents of the 3rd mixing bowl.
Pour contents of the 3rd mixing bowl into the baking dish.
Pour contents of the 2nd mixing bowl into the baking dish.
Pour contents of the mixing bowl into the baking dish.

Serves 1.
